"ru\" href=\"/ru\">RU</a><span class=\"text-gray-600\">/</span><a class=\"text-sm font-medium transition text-teal-500\" hrefLang=\"uz\" href=\"/uz\">UZ</a></div></nav><div class=\"hidden md:flex flex-col items-end space-y-1\"><a href=\"tel:+998770802288\" class=\"text-white font-semibold hover:text-teal-500 transition text-sm\">+998 77 080 22 88</a><a href=\"tel:+998974802288\" class=\"text-gray-300 text-xs hover:text-teal-500 transition\">+998 97 480 22 88</a></div><button class=\"lg:hidden text-white p-2\" aria-label=\"Открыть меню\" aria-expanded=\"false\" aria-controls=\"mobile-navigation\"><svg class=\"w-6 h-6\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\"><path stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-width=\"2\" d=\"M4 6h16M4 12h16M4 18h16\"></path></svg></button></div></div></header><main id=\"main-content\" class=\"pt-20\"><script type=\"application/ld+json\">{\"@context\":\"https://schema.org\",\"@type\":\"Article\",\"headline\":\"Keys: Welcome Pack eNPSni 23% oshirdi - Toshkent\",\"description\":\"Welcome pack natijalari: eNPS +23%. Tarkib, jarayon va HR fikri. Hisob-kitob so'rang!\",\"url\":\"https://graver-studio.uz/uz/blog/keys-welcome-pack-povysil-enps-v-it-kompanii-uz\",\"image\":\"/images/blog/keys-welcome-pack-povysil-enps-v-it-kompanii-uz.jpg\",\"datePublished\":\"2026-03-03\",\"dateModified\":\"2026-03-03\",\"author\":{\"@type\":\"Organization\",\"name\":\"Graver.uz\",\"url\":\"https://graver-studio.uz\"},\"publisher\":{\"@type\":\"Organization\",\"name\":\"Graver.uz\",\"logo\":{\"@type\":\"ImageObject\",\"url\":\"https://graver-studio.uz/logo192.png\"}},\"mainEntityOfPage\":{\"@type\":\"WebPage\",\"@id\":\"https://graver-studio.uz/uz/blog/keys-welcome-pack-povysil-enps-v-it-kompanii-uz\"}}</script><script type=\"application/ld+json\">{\"@context\":\"https://schema.org\",\"@type\":\"BreadcrumbList\",\"itemListElement\":[{\"@type\":\"ListItem\",\"position\":1,\"name\":\"Graver.uz\",\"item\":\"https://graver-studio.uz/uz\"},{\"@type\":\"ListItem\",\"position\":2,\"name\":\"Blog\",\"item\":\"https://graver-studio.uz/uz/blog\"},{\"@type\":\"ListItem\",\"position\":3,\"name\":\"Keys: Welcome Pack eNPSni 23% oshirdi - Toshkent\",\"item\":\"https://graver-studio.uz/uz/blog/keys-welcome-pack-povysil-enps-v-it-kompanii-uz\"}]}</script><div class=\"max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-12\"><nav aria-label=\"breadcrumb\" class=\"mb-8\"><ol class=\"flex items-center space-x-2 text-sm text-gray-400 flex-wrap gap-y-1\"><li><a class=\"hover:text-teal-500\" href=\"/uz\">Graver.uz</a></li><li class=\"text-gray-600\">/</li><li><a class=\"hover:text-teal-500\" href=\"/uz/blog\">Blog</a></li><li class=\"text-gray-600\">/</li><li class=\"text-gray-300 truncate max-w-xs\">Keys: Welcome Pack eNPSni 23% oshirdi - Toshkent</li></ol></nav><header class=\"mb-10\"><h1 class=\"text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-white mb-4 leading-tight\">Keys: Welcome Pack eNPSni 23% oshirdi - Toshkent</h1><div class=\"flex items-center space-x-4 text-sm text-gray-500\"><time dateTime=\"2026-03-03\">2-mart, 2026</time><span>3<!-- --> <!-- -->daqiqa o&#x27;qish</span><span>Graver.uz</span></div></header><div class=\"mb-10 rounded-xl overflow-hidden\"><img src=\"/images/blog/keys-welcome-pack-povysil-enps-v-it-kompanii-uz.jpg\" alt=\"Keys: Welcome Pack eNPSni 23% oshirdi - Toshkent\" class=\"w-full aspect-video object-cover\" loading=\"eager\"/></div><article class=\"prose prose-invert max-w-none\"><p>Agar onboarding &quot;birinchi kun&quot; bilan tugasa, xodimning ichki motivatsiyasi esa 3-4 haftada so&#x27;nadi. Ushbu keysda Toshkentdagi IT-kompaniya welcome pack orqali yangi xodimlarda &quot;men bu yerga tegishliman&quot; hissini kuchaytirib, eNPS ko&#x27;rsatkichini sezilarli yaxshiladi.</p>\n<h2>Muammo: yangi xodimlar sovuq start olardi</h2>\n<p>HR jamoasi uchta og&#x27;riq nuqtani ko&#x27;rdi: (1) birinchi haftada stress yuqori, (2) ichki kommunikatsiya sekin, (3) &quot;qabul qilinish&quot; hissi yetishmaydi. Natijada onboarding jarayoni uzayadi, savollar ko&#x27;payadi, birinchi 30 kunda xatolar ko&#x27;p uchraydi.</p>\n<h2>Maqsad: yangi xodimni birinchi kundan brendga &quot;ulash&quot;, kundalik ishga tezroq kiritish va ijobiy emosiyani mustahkamlash.</h2>\n<h2>Nima buyurtma qilindi: 3 darajali welcome pack konsepti</h2>\n<p>Kompaniya uchta profilni ajratdi: junior/middle, senior va lead/management. Har biri uchun umumiy brend elementlari + rolga mos foydali buyumlar tanlandi.</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Bir xil vizual kod: ranglar, minimalistik dizayn, bitta &quot;unboxing&quot; ssenariysi</li>\n<li>Har bir buyumda lazer gravirovka: logo, ism, lavozim yoki qisqa shior</li>\n<li>Qadoqlash: &quot;premium, ammo ortiqcha dabdaba emas&quot;</li>\n</ul>\n<h2>Jarayon: brifdan yetkazib berishgacha 10 kun</h2>\n<p>Graver Studio bilan ish jarayoni 4 bosqichga bo&#x27;lindi: brif → maket → ishlab chiqarish → QC + yetkazish. Toshkent ichida logistika va yig&#x27;ish jarayoni alohida nazorat qilindi, shunda HRga &quot;qo&#x27;lda yig&#x27;ish&quot; yuklamasi tushmadi.</p>\n<ol>\n<li><strong>Brif (1 kun)</strong></li>\n</ol>\n<ul>\n<li>xodimlar soni va rollar bo&#x27;yicha taqsimot</li>\n<li>byudjet diapazoni va &quot;must-have&quot; buyumlar</li>\n<li>brend qo&#x27;llanmasi: rang, shrift, logo variantlari</li>\n<li>gravirovka formatlari: logo/ism/QR-kod</li>\n</ul>\n<ol start=\"2\">\n<li><strong>Maket va tasdiqlash (1-2 kun)</strong></li>\n</ol>\n<ul>\n<li>3 ta mockup varianti</li>\n<li>ism yozilishi (transliteratsiya) bo&#x27;yicha ro&#x27;yxat</li>\n<li>qadoqlash yorlig&#x27;i va tabrik kartasi matni</li>\n</ul>\n<ol start=\"3\">\n<li><strong>Ishlab chiqarish (5-6 kun)</strong>&gt;Asosiy texnologiya - lazer gravirovka. U logotipni aniq, toza va uzoq saqlanadigan qiladi, ayniqsa metall va yog&#x27;och yuzalarda.</li>\n<li><strong>QC va yetkazib berish (1 kun)</strong></li>\n</ol>\n<ul>\n<li>namuna bilan solishtirib tekshiruv</li>\n<li>qadoqlash, komplektatsiya, ro&#x27;yxat bo&#x27;yicha nazorat</li>\n<li>ofisga yetkazib berish, akt</li>\n</ul>\n<h2>Nabor tarkibi: &quot;nima bor edi?&quot;</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>Metall termo-krujka yoki termos (logo + ism lazer gravirovka)</li>\n<li>Brendli daftar + metal ruchka (ruchkada gravirovka)</li>\n<li>USB/Type-C adapter yoki kabel-organayzer</li>\n<li>ID-karta uchun lanyard yoki badge-holder</li>\n<li>Stikerlar to&#x27;plami (brend ikonlari)</li>\n<li>Tabrik kartasi: &quot;birinchi hafta yo&#x27;l xaritasi&quot;</li>\n<li>Premium quti + ichki to&#x27;ldirgich (qadoqlash)</li>\n</ul>\n<p><em>Eslatma: Quyidagi pozitsiyalar - amaliy misol. Sizning brifingizga qarab tarkib o&#x27;zgaradi.</em></p>\n<h2>Natija: eNPS +23% va onboarding hissiyotining o&#x27;zgarishi</h2>\n<p>Welcome pack joriy qilingandan so&#x27;ng ichki so&#x27;rovnomada eNPS ko&#x27;rsatkichi 23% ga oshdi. HR jamoasi eng katta o&#x27;zgarishni &quot;birinchi kun&quot; taassurotida va jamoaga moslashuv tezligida qayd etdi.</p>\n<h3>HR fikri (qisqa iqtibos)</h3>\n<p>&quot;Avval yangi xodimlar o&#x27;zini mehmondek his qilardi. Endi esa birinchi kundan &#x27;men shu jamoaning bir qismiman&#x27; degan signalni oladi. Eng zo&#x27;ri - hammasi standart, ammo shaxsiy.&quot;</p>\n<h3>Qaysi elementlar eng ko&#x27;p &quot;ta&#x27;sir qildi&quot;</h3>\n<ul>\n<li>Ism bilan gravirovka (shaxsiylashtirish)</li>\n<li>Unboxing ssenariysi (quti ichidagi tartib)</li>\n<li>&quot;Birinchi hafta yo&#x27;l xaritasi&quot; kartasi (amaliy qiymat)</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Buyurtma bermoqchimisiz?</strong> Telegram <a href=\"https://t.me/graveruz\">@graveruz</a> ga yozing yoki saytdagi shaklni to&#x27;ldiring.</p></article><section class=\"mt-12 border-t border-gray-800 pt-10\"><h2 class=\"text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-6\">O&#x27;xshash maqolalar</h2><div class=\"grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-6\"><article class=\"bg-gray-800/50 rounded-xl p-5 border border-gray-700 hover:border-teal-500 transition\"><h3 class=\"text-base font-semibold text-white mb-2 line-clamp-2\"><a class=\"hover:text-teal-500 transition\" href=\"/uz/blog/welcome-pack-yangi-xodimlar\">Yangi xodimlar uchun Welcome Pack</a></h3><p class=\"text-gray-400 text-sm line-clamp-2\">Welcome Pack tuzish bo&#x27;yicha qo&#x27;llanma: tarkibi, brendlash, tashkil etish. HR uchun amaliy maslahatlar.</p></article><article class=\"bg-gray-800/50 rounded-xl p-5 border border-gray-700 hover:border-teal-500 transition\"><h3 class=\"text-base font-semibold text-white mb-2 line-clamp-2\"><a class=\"hover:text-teal-500 transition\" href=\"/uz/blog/it-kompaniyalar-uchun-merch-toshkent\">Toshkentdagi IT-kompaniyalar uchun merch: Qanday qilib ajralib turish va HR-brendni kuchaytirish</a></h3><p class=\"text-gray-400 text-sm line-clamp-2\">Toshkentdagi IT-kompaniyalar uchun premium merch: xudi, powerbank, welcome pack va lazerli gravyura. Ishlab chiqarishdan oldin maket.</p></article><article class=\"bg-gray-800/50 rounded-xl p-5 border border-gray-700 hover:border-teal-500 transition\"><h3 class=\"text-base font-semibold text-white mb-2 line-clamp-2\"><a class=\"hover:text-teal-500 transition\" href=\"/uz/blog/xodimlar-sadoqati-korporativ-sovgalar\">Korporativ sovg&#x27;alar kadrlar oqimini qanday kamaytiradi | Graver Studio</a></h3><p class=\"text-gray-400 text-sm line-clamp-2\">Korporativ sovg&#x27;alar orqali xodimlar sadoqatini oshirish va kadrlar oqimini kamaytirish: strategiya, misollar va ROI.</p></article></div></section><div class=\"mt-12 border-t border-gray-800 pt-8\"><a class=\"text-teal-500 hover:text-teal-400 transition flex items-center\" href=\"/uz/blog\">← <!-- -->Blogga qaytish</a></div></div></main><footer class=\"bg-black border-t border-gray-800 mt-20\"><div class=\"max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-12\"><div class=\"grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-8\"><div><a class=\"flex items-center space-x-2 mb-4\" href=\"/uz\"><div class=\"w-8 h-8 bg-gradient-to-br from-teal-500 to-cyan-600 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center\"><span class=\"text-white font-bold\