s-center justify-center px-4\",\"children\":[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"text-center\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"h1\",null,{\"className\":\"text-8xl font-bold text-teal-500 mb-4\",\"children\":\"404\"}],[\"$\",\"h2\",null,{\"className\":\"text-2xl font-semibold text-white mb-4\",\"children\":\"Страница не найдена\"}],[\"$\",\"p\",null,{\"className\":\"text-gray-400 mb-8\",\"children\":\"Запрошенная страница не существует.\"}],[\"$\",\"$L12\",null,{\"href\":\"/ru\",\"className\":\"bg-gradient-to-r from-teal-500 to-cyan-600 text-white px-6 py-3 rounded-lg font-semibold hover:opacity-90 transition\",\"children\":\"На главную\"}]]}]}]\n13:[[\"$\",\"p\",null,{\"children\":\"Agar onboarding \\\"birinchi kun\\\" bilan tugasa, xodimning ichki motivatsiyasi esa 3-4 haftada so'nadi. Ushbu keysda Toshkentdagi IT-kompaniya welcome pack orqali yangi xodimlarda \\\"men bu yerga tegishliman\\\" hissini kuchaytirib, eNPS ko'rsatkichini sezilarli yaxshiladi.\"}],\"\\n\",[\"$\",\"h2\",null,{\"children\":\"Muammo: yangi xodimlar sovuq start olardi\"}],\"\\n\",[\"$\",\"p\",null,{\"children\":\"HR jamoasi uchta og'riq nuqtani ko'rdi: (1) birinchi haftada stress yuqori, (2) ichki kommunikatsiya sekin, (3) \\\"qabul qilinish\\\" hissi yetishmaydi. Natijada onboarding jarayoni uzayadi, savollar ko'payadi, birinchi 30 kunda xatolar ko'p uchraydi.\"}],\"\\n\",[\"$\",\"h2\",null,{\"children\":\"Maqsad: yangi xodimni birinchi kundan brendga \\\"ulash\\\", kundalik ishga tezroq kiritish va ijobiy emosiyani mustahkamlash.\"}],\"\\n\",[\"$\",\"h2\",null,{\"children\":\"Nima buyurtma qilindi: 3 darajali welcome pack konsepti\"}],\"\\n\",[\"$\",\"p\",null,{\"children\":\"Kompaniya uchta profilni ajratdi: junior/middle, senior va lead/management. Har biri uchun umumiy brend elementlari + rolga mos foydali buyumlar tanlandi.\"}],\"\\n\",[\"$\",\"ul\",null,{\"children\":[\"\\n\",[\"$\",\"li\",null,{\"children\":\"Bir xil vizual kod: ranglar, minimalistik dizayn, bitta \\\"unboxing\\\" ssenariysi\"}],\"\\n\",[\"$\",\"li\",null,{\"children\":\"Har bir buyumda lazer gravirovka: logo, ism, lavozim yoki qisqa shior\"}],\"\\n\",[\"$\",\"li\",null,{\"children\":\"Qadoqlash: \\\"premium, ammo ortiqcha dabdaba emas\\\"\"}],\"\\n\"]}],\"\\n\",[\"$\",\"h2\",null,{\"children\":\"Jarayon: brifdan yetkazib berishgacha 10 kun\"}],\"\\n\",[\"$\",\"p\",null,{\"children\":\"Graver Studio bilan ish jarayoni 4 bosqichga bo'lindi: brif → maket → ishlab chiqarish → QC + yetkazish. Toshkent ichida logistika va yig'ish jarayoni alohida nazorat qilindi, shunda HRga \\\"qo'lda yig'ish\\\" yuklamasi tushmadi.\"}],\"\\n\",[\"$\",\"ol\",null,{\"children\":[\"\\n\",[\"$\",\"li\",null,{\"children\":[\"$\",\"strong\",null,{\"children\":\"Brif (1 kun)\"}]}],\"\\n\"]}],\"\\n\",[\"$\",\"ul\",null,{\"children\":[\"\\n\",[\"$\",\"li\",null,{\"children\":\"xodimlar soni va rollar bo'yicha taqsimot\"}],\"\\n\",[\"$\",\"li\",null,{\"children\":\"byudjet diapazoni va \\\"must-have\\\" buyumlar\"}],\"\\n\",[\"$\",\"li\",null,{\"children\":\"brend qo'llanmasi: rang, shrift, logo variantlari\"}],\"\\n\",[\"$\",\"li\",null,{\"children\":\"gravirovka formatlari: logo/ism/QR-kod\"}],\"\\n\"]}],\"\\n\",[\"$\",\"ol\",null,{\"start\":\"2\",\"children\":[\"\\n\",[\"$\",\"li\",null,{\"children\":[\"$\",\"strong\",null,{\"children\":\"Maket va tasdiqlash (1-2 kun)\"}]}],\"\\n\"]}],\"\\n\",[\"$\",\"ul\",null,{\"children\":[\"\\n\",[\"$\",\"li\",null,{\"children\":\"3 ta mockup varianti\"}],\"\\n\",[\"$\",\"li\",null,{\"children\":\"ism yozilishi (transliteratsiya) bo'yicha ro'yxat\"}],\"\\n\",[\"$\",\"li\",null,{\"children\":\"qadoqlash yorlig'i va tabrik kartasi matni\"}],\"\\n\"]}],\"\\n\",[\"$\",\"ol\",null,{\"start\":\"3\",\"children\":[\"\\n\",[\"$\",\"li\",null,{\"children\":[[\"$\",\"strong\",null,{\"children\":\"Ishlab chiqarish (5-6 kun)\"}],\">Asosiy texnologiya - lazer gravirovka. U logotipni aniq, toza va uzoq saqlanadigan qiladi, ayniqsa metall va yog'och yuzalarda.\"]}],\"\\n\",[\"$\",\"li\",null,{\"children\":[\"$\",\"strong\",null,{\"children\":\"QC va yetkazib berish (1 kun)\"}]}],\"\\n\"]}],\"\\n\",[\"$\",\"ul\",null,{\"children\":[\"\\n\",[\"$\",\"li\",null,{\"children\":\"namuna bilan solishtirib tekshiruv\"}],\"\\n\",[\"$\",\"li\",null,{\"children\":\"qadoqlash, komplektatsiya, ro'yxat bo'yicha nazorat\"}],\"\\n\",[\"$\",\"li\",null,{\"children\":\"ofisga yetkazib berish, akt\"}],\"\\n\"]}],\"\\n\",[\"$\",\"h2\",null,{\"children\":\"Nabor tarkibi: \\\"nima bor edi?\\\"\"}],\"\\n\",[\"$\",\"ul\",null,{\"children\":[\"\\n\",[\"$\",\"li\",null,{\"children\":\"Metall termo-krujka yoki termos (logo + ism lazer gravirovka)\"}],\"\\n\",[\"$\",\"li\",null,{\"children\":\"Brendli daftar + metal ruchka (ruchkada gravirovka)\"}],\"\\n\",[\"$\",\"li\",null,{\"children\":\"USB/Type-C adapter yoki kabel-organayzer\"}],\"\\n\",[\"$\",\"li\",null,{\"children\":\"ID-karta uchun lanyard yoki badge-holder\"}],\"\\n\",[\"$\",\"li\",null,{\"children\":\"Stikerlar to'plami (brend ikonlari)\"}],\"\\n\",[\"$\",\"li\",null,{\"children\":\"Tabrik kartasi: \\\"birinchi hafta yo'l xaritasi\\\"\"}],\"\\n\",[\"$\",\"li\",null,{\"children\":\"Premium quti + ichki to'ldirgich (qadoqlash)\"}],\"\\n\"]}],\"\\n\",[\"$\",\"p\",null,{\"children\":[\"$\",\"em\",null,{\"children\":\"Eslatma: Quyidagi pozitsiyalar - amaliy misol. Sizning brifingizga qarab tarkib o'zgaradi.\"}]}],\"\\n\",[\"$\",\"h2\",null,{\"children\":\"Natija: eNPS +23% va onboarding hissiyotining o'zgarishi\"}],\"\\n\",[\"$\",\"p\",null,{\"children\":\"Welcome pack joriy qilingandan so'ng ichki so'rovnomada eNPS ko'rsatkichi 23% ga oshdi. HR jamoasi eng katta o'zgarishni \\\"birinchi kun\\\" taassurotida va jamoaga moslashuv tezligida qayd etdi.\"}],\"\\n\",[\"$\",\"h3\",null,{\"children\":\"HR fikri (qisqa iqtibos)\"}],\"\\n\",[\"$\",\"p\",null,{\"children\":\"\\\"Avval yangi xodimlar o'zini mehmondek his qilardi. Endi esa birinchi kundan 'men shu jamoaning bir qismiman' degan signalni oladi. Eng zo'ri - hammasi standart, ammo shaxsiy.\\\"\"}],\"\\n\",[\"$\",\"h3\",null,{\"children\":\"Qaysi elementlar eng ko'p \\\"ta'sir qildi\\\"\"}],\"\\n\",[\"$\",\"ul\",null,{\"children\":[\"\\n\",[\"$\",\"li\",null,{\"children\":\"Ism bilan gravirovka (shaxsiylashtirish)\"}],\"\\n\",[\"$\",\"li\",null,{\"children\":\"Unboxing ssenariysi (quti ichidagi tartib)\"}],\"\\n\",[\"$\",\"li\",null,{\"children\":\"\\\"Birinchi hafta yo'l xaritasi\\\" kartasi (amaliy qiymat)\"}],\"\\n\"]}],\"\\n\",[\"$\",\"p\",null,{\"children\":[[\"$\",\"strong\",null,{\"children\":\"Buyurtma bermoqchimisiz?\"}],\" Telegram \",[\"$\",\"a\",null,{\"href\":\"https://t.me/graveruz\",\"children\":\"@graveruz\"}],\" ga yozing yoki saytdagi shaklni to'ldiring.\"]}]]\nb:[[\"$\",\"meta\",\"0\",{\"charSet\":\"utf-8\"}],[\"$\",\"meta\",\"1\",{\"name\":\"viewport\",\"content\":\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1\"}],[\"$\",\"meta\",\"2\",{\"name\":\"theme-color\",\"content\":\"#14b8a6\"}]]\n8:null\n9:null\nd:[[\"$\",\"title\",\"0\",{\"children\":\"Keys: Welcome Pack eNPSni 23% oshirdi - Toshkent | Graver.uz\"}],[\"$\",\"meta\",\"1\",{\"name\":\"description\",\"content\":\"Welcome pack natijalari: eNPS +23%. Tarkib, jarayon va HR fikri. Hisob-kitob so'rang!\"}],[\"$\",\"link\",\"2\",{\"rel\":\"canonical\",\"href\":\"https://graver-studio.uz/uz/blog/keys-welcome-pack-povysil-enps-v-it-kompanii-uz\"}],[\"$\",\"link\",\"3\",{\"rel\":\"alternate\",\"hrefLang\":\"ru\",\"href\":\"https://graver-studio.uz/ru/blog/keys-welcome-pack-povysil-enps-v-it-kompanii\"}],[\"$\",\"link\",\"4\",{\"rel\":\"alternate\",\"hrefLang\":\"uz\",\"href\":\"https://graver-studio.uz/uz/blog/keys-welcome-pack-povysil-enps-v-it-kompanii-uz\"}],[\"$\",\"link\",\"5\",{\"rel\":\"alternate\",\"hrefLang\":\"x-default\",\"href\":\"https://graver-studio.uz/ru/blog/keys-welcome-pack-povysil-enps-v-it-kompanii-uz\"}],[\"$\",\"meta\",\"6\",{\"property\":\"og:title\",\"content\":\"Keys: Welcome Pack eNPSni 23% oshirdi - Toshkent\"}],[\"$\",\"meta\",\"7\",{\"property\":